{
  "texts": [
    "Additionally, models like TG-LLM (Xiong et al., 2024) and chain-of-thought (CoT) reasoning enhance LLMs' ability to comprehend complex temporal logic.",
    "Furthermore, generative temporal question-answering frameworks (GenTKGQA) (Gao et al., 2024) achieve efficient reasoning by combining subgraph retrieval with virtual knowledge integration.",
    "Future research will focus on optimizing temporal data representation, improving cross-domain generalization, and deeply modeling temporal logic and causal relationships to advance the intelligence and efficiency of temporal reasoning in AI.",
    "As shown in Figure 15, the integration of knowledge graphs (KGs) and large language models (LLMs) has been successfully applied in five key fields: (1) medical, (2) industrial, (3) education, (4) financial, and (5) legal.",
    "In the medical domain, the integration of KGs and LLMs has shown immense potential for improving various healthcare applications."
  ]
}